@baseUrl = http://localhost:7070/product

### Get All Products

GET {{baseUrl}}/all

### Get Product with ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create new Product

POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productName" : "Test Prodcut Iphone",
    "userId" : 1
}

### Update Product on ID

PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productName" : "Updated Test Iphone",
    "userId" : "1",
    "warrantyId" : "1"
}

### Delete Product on ID

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1